c: 4
v: 19
t: "Yemwe abemeye! Muziririjwe kuzungura abagore ku gahato, kandi ntimukabagore (mubabuza kongera gushakwa) kugira ngo mubambure bimwe mu byo mwabahaye; keretse baramutse bakoze icyaha kigaragara (nk’ubusambanyi cyangwa gusuzugura abagabo babo), kandi mujye mubana na bo neza. Nimugira icyo mubanenga (mujye mwihangana), kuko hari ubwo mwakwanga ikintu Allah akaba ari cyo ashyiramo ibyiza byinshi"